race.comment: MANEUVER EXPRESS (4) looks close to another win after finishing third last time (21.11) in a Grade 5 at this track. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Makes plenty of appeal. INTEGRITY BET (3) is better than last start when sixth (21.53) from Box 2 at this track over 365m. Form from his last run is proving strong. Better than last start and can bounce back. CASCADE MISS (1) looks close to another win after finishing second from Box 3 last time (20.95) at this track. Can measure up. SPUNKY MONKEY (2) jumps at a shorter distance and still warrants respect.
